  </sec>
  <sec>
    <title>CONCLUSIONS AND FUTURE DIRECTIONS</title>
    <p>PVS is a user-friendly and versatile web server where sequence variability computations are exploited to facilitate structure-function studies and, unlike any other related server, <italic>de novo</italic> epitope discovery. In the future, we plan to include additional variability and conservation scores. Moreover, we will implement solvent accessibility calculations, which should enhance the potential of PVS in structure–function studies and B-cell epitope discovery.</p>
  </sec>
